General.Name: Tanke Incorporated
General.Description: Tanke, Inc., through its subsidiaries, develops and markets environmental and water technologies. The company offers Tripple R Water Recycling for the reclamation, treatment, and recycling of wastewater or storm water collected from homes, commercial buildings and industrial facilities; and Tripple R Water Recycling, a water recycling system for hotels, dry kitchens, and buildings. It also provides uSMART, a Software-as-a-Service enterprise resource planning proprietary software technology. Tanke, Inc. was formerly known as LP Holdings Inc. and changed its name to Tanke, Inc. in 2007. The company was incorporated in 1984 and is based in Las Vegas, Nevada.
